title: Alphabet Soup - Melissa Doyle
description:
Australia's best loved morning TV presenter, Mel Doyle, invites you inside her home and her life. Now, for the first time, Mel shares what it is like to juggle a high profile TV career with the full time job of being a Mum.

In Alphabet Soup, she has collected together some of her favourite memories and anecdotes from the last ten years. Covering everything from her relationship with Kochie to red carpet exclusives, from baking birthday cakes to doing the school run, this is a delicious slice of Mel's life. And, like the rest of us, Mel has highs and lows and a constant battle to balance it all out.

Dip in and enjoy some funny, honest and totally relatable anecdotes from life on and off screen!
